Updated November     pm



Jungkook is set to release 3D featuring Jack Harlow this week PERIOD

The BTS star teased his new solo song with a video teaser during his performance at the  Global Citizen Festival in New York at the weekend PERIOD

Big Hit Music later confirmed that the track with the First Class hitmaker is dropping on Friday .. whilst describing it as a pop RnB track with clever expressions of feelings toward an unattainable person from the perspectives of first second and third dimensions. the label has also shared a series of visuals in promotion of the new tune PERIOD

The star recently released his debut solo single Seven with American rapper Latto PERIOD

And hes set to release a  by November PERIOD

Speaking to his BTS bandmate Suga on his talk show Suchwita Jungkook teased I have another single PERIOD And then Ill be releasing a small mini album by November.more appreciated and be even betterIn a word cool PERIOD Thats the whole reason Im doing this PERIOD I want to be that kind of pop star someday  I want to be able to really experience that feeling.. PERIOD

I hope the day comes that I can look at myself from a thirdperson perspective and give myself that kind of recognition PERIOD
